summary: New face for brave huntress. Still lore-friendly, I believe.
descriptionHtml:
Description:
My another face editing work. I figured out that only ranged follower (who has a marriage possibility :3) who have an alignment appropriate to my male character is Aela. But her face model has always made me sad. So I\'ve decided to make my own version of dat wild huntress and here it is.
This time I wasn\'t used any presets to change her face - she was made from scratch.

Advertisement:
If you like my version of Aela, check out my another work - [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=16628]Lydia edited[/url].

Requirements:
No other mods required for proper work. But for exact match with the screenshots you should install [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666]Caliente\'s CBBE (both body and face pack)[/url] with [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=13377]Sporty body texture[/url] and [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=515]More Freckles[/url]. \"Title\" screenshot was made with [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=15105]Sharpshooters Extreme Graphics Vision ENB[/url] enabled.

Credits:
Thanks for creators of all mods listed above and special thanks to c_striker for his [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=15963]Expanded Skyrim Presets[/url] which inspired me to do this \"edit\" mods.
author: Utherien
